  "title": "SRE Teaching \u2014 SLO & Error Budget",
  "uid": "sre-slo-error-budget",
  "version": 1,
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## SLI, SLO, Error Budget\n\n- **SLI** (Indicator) \u2014 A measurable aspect of reliability (e.g. % successful requests)\n- **SLO** (Objective) \u2014 Target for the SLI (e.g. 99.9% availability over 30 days)\n- **Error budget** \u2014 Allowed unreliability: `1 - SLO` (99.9% \u2192 0.1% bad requests)\n\n**Burn rate:** How fast you consume the budget. Fast burn \u2192 page immediately. Slow burn \u2192 ticket.\n\nThis dashboard uses a **99.9% availability SLO** on HTTP success (non-5xx). Adjust targets in panels for your team agreement.\n\n**Exercise:** If availability SLI is 99.95% but SLO is 99.9%, you still have budget. At 99.5%, you've exhausted budget \u2014 freeze features, focus on reliability.\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "gauge",
      "title": "Availability SLI (5m window)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.995
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0.999
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "1 - (\n  sum(rate(http_requests_total{namespace=\"ecommerce\",status=~\"5..\"}[5m]))\n  / sum(rate(http_requests_total{namespace=\"ecommerce\"}[5m]))\n)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "SLO target",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
