      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Multi-window burn alerts** (Google SRE Workbook): Compare short and long windows \u2014 e.g. 5m and 1h \u2014 to catch both sudden incidents and gradual degradation without alert fatigue.\n\nPrometheusRule alerts in `ecommerce-app-rules` implement symptom thresholds: `EcommerceHighErrorRate` (>5% 5xx), `EcommerceHighLatency` (p95 > 1s).\n"
      }
